Module mesakit.graph.core
Package com.telenav.mesakit.graph.collections

Class RelationSet

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.collections.RelationSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<EdgeRelation>, Collection<EdgeRelation>, Set<EdgeRelation>
public class RelationSet extends Object implements Set<EdgeRelation>
A set of relations. Supports union(RelationSet) and without(Set) operations, that logically combine this set of relations with another set of relations without creating a physical set.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
